{
  "stem": "20405.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Over there, they died-- so many people they die [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and-- because was full of lice, contaminated water from typhus.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And over there, died the second brother of this Raul I told you, the German shot him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He died from tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was near to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He die over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't care about tuberculosis or nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He died right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And from there-- from there it was one week, two weeks, I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So somebody brought us some packages from the Red Cross, chocolate in it, a few canned goods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So one package for three, four person, five, six person, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we got some real food from this package from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we woke up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We hear that Hitler dies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He killed himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And over there was not wires around, were only the guards from that Wehrmacht, not SS, because if they were an SS, maybe they were going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Was the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we see them-- we didn't see them anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When we didn't see them anymore, with a couple of friends of mine we start walking, going the way the Americans were coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going, going, going, going, going, going like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't see no Americans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stopped in a little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a barn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the barn, we went up on top of the upstairs of the barn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over there were some chickens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I'm laying down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was burning a fever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I told my friend, go ahead and get one chicken.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Make-- boil it to have a chicken soup, something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, he didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
